snippet.title: Super Rocket Pets: Official Trailer
snippet.description:
DOWNLOAD FOR FREE NOW!!!
Apple App Store: http://apple.co/1Wtkfnb
Android Store: http://bit.ly/1NXsy42

The Rocket Pets are blasting off through a galaxy not so far, far away. These flying fur balls are on a thrilling quest for coins. Explore the beautiful planets as you try to travel as far as possible in this action platform game. Customize your wonderful pets as you see fit, upgrade their gear and beat your previous records in Rocket Pets!

http://rocketpets.massivemonster.co.uk
